WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:48.000
 Remove air filter bolts. 

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:51.000
 Lift air filter up. 

00:00:51.000 --> 00:01:06.000
 Remove bolts. 

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:10.000
 Remove the oil cap. 

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.000
 Remove the hood. 

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:53.000
 Disassemble bolt crankcase cap. 

00:01:53.000 --> 00:02:06.000
 Disassemble crankcase cover. (make sure nothing falls into the oil tank !!) 

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:34.000
 Install blocking key. 

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:46.000
 Remove the coupling housing nut. 

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:50.000
 Disassemble the clutch housing. 

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:53.000
 Mount blocking key on rear coupling. 

00:02:53.000 --> 00:03:02.000
 Remove the nut. 

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:27.000
 Put new V-belt in rear coupling. (Note: pull the bowls of the pulley as far apart as possible. This is difficult !!) 

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:35.000
 Replace the clutch pulley. 

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:51.000
 Fit nut. 

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:54.000
 Fit V-belt on crankshaft. 

00:03:54.000 --> 00:04:17.000
 Mount cooling fin vario. 

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:45.000
 Fit washers and nut. 

00:04:45.000 --> 00:05:02.000
 Disassemble blocking key. 

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:07.000
 Install crankcase cover. 

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:35.000
 Fit bolts with grease. 

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:58.000
 Install air filter. 

